    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>SlideSnap v1.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Click on a slide's background color to auto-detect and capture it</li>
          <li>Drag-to-select fallback for manual cropping</li>
          <li>Copies to clipboard (Universal Clipboard compatible)</li>
          <li>Saves to ~/Documents/SlideSnap/</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
